<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى النمل:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{لَقَدْ وُعِدْنا هذا نَحْنُ وَآباؤُنا}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النمل:٦٨]</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٤٠]</span> فى القصص: <span style="color:#947721">{وَجاءَ رَجُلٌ مِنْ أَقْصَى الْمَدِينَةِ يَسْعى}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[القصص:٢٠]</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى يس:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَجاءَ مِنْ أَقْصَا الْمَدِينَةِ رَجُلٌ يَسْعى}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[يس:٢٠]</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
