<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٤٤]</span> وفى الرعد: <span style="color:#947721">{لا يَمْلِكُونَ لِأَنْفُسِهِمْ نَفْعاً وَلا ضَرًّا}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الرعد:١٦]</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٤٥]</span> وفى الأنبياء: <span style="color:#947721">{ما لا يَنْفَعُكُمْ شَيْئاً وَلا يَضُرُّكُمْ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الأنبياء:٦٦]</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
